title: 2012 O'Neill Heat Wetsuit
description: The Heat is stuffed with all new high-end features and materials: Built with 100% ultra gooey UltraFlex DS Neoprene. Along with our X-Type Firewall in the chest and back make this suit warmer and more flexible than its predecessor. The Heat also includes exterior Fluid Seam Weld, redesigned zipper panel, Covert/ Code Red Zipper, new graphics and easy-in-easy-out usability.
